{"type": "article", "id": 24410, "title": "英国网球品牌 Fred Perry 在东京开出了最大的旗舰店", "description": "店铺和这个品牌一样简洁优雅。\r\n", "date": "2016-03-25T07:01:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1702, "name": "网球"}, {"id": 32, "name": "时尚"}, {"id": 25351, "name": "Fred Perry"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021313000doXpeJnutg1qO3I.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>英国的网球品牌 <a href=\"http://www.fredperry.com\">Fred Perry </a>于 3 月 19 日在东京神宫前开设一家旗舰店，也是他们最大的旗舰店。</p>\n<p class=\"\">熟悉网球的人也许记得弗雷德·佩里（Frederick John Perry，1909 年 5 月 18 日－1995 年 2 月 2 日），他是英国网球史上最重要的运动员之一。早年是乒乓球运动员，在 1929 年获得了世界乒乓球锦标赛男单冠军，但随后转入网球运动，在 1930 年代获得过 8 次大满贯。二战结束后，他和奥地利足球员 Tibby Wegner  一起创立了网球品牌  Fred Perry ，以运动服饰为主，吸收了英伦风格的简洁优雅和英国流行文化，后来成为休闲服饰，也受到年轻人的喜爱。</p>\n<p>这家在东京的旗舰店有 3 层楼，大概 3500 平方尺（388.9 平方米），外墙很像英国工业革命时的工厂，实际是从爱知县订制的 45,000 块深红色窑烧砖，看起来严谨规整。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021312442OhC8qeGLgulf9tF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131244gQn5qizVeh6YUd1M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131245j1x2iuZYKQpkgWz8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">入口处用薄木片排列出的月桂形 logo，后面延伸了至少 5 米长，形成一个前台的接待柜。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131245mGA763BUVMxt0bfq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021312465aqj6OY3TemksZ2W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94347826\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131246i6WcdLhvP4DR5ZzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>室内也有工厂的空旷感，有大面积的挑高，用楼梯连接相互的错层。黑色金属出现在窗框、楼梯扶手、灯架和衣架上，与白色墙面相对，让店铺显得非常干净。室内出售的衣服并不多，也留出了大量的空位。</p>\n<p class=\"\">不过，仍然可以从不同的区域里看到大致的划分，最低一层集中放了衣服，靠墙处有整齐的木柜出售包。在二楼的一个区域是经典款的衣服，它们被装在了透明的玻璃盒子里作为展示。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131247wrXQiqx6kMTyo3U9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98115942\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021312479FinxwDdgUL4W2CK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131248m8Bj6UqVLy9gxbJu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131248ZneQtcT45Xw2SKDG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131249XVofM6lCGRw4mH0A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131249ZnN8D5fF1zB7jteS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131250y1nN97TYQd24ZMg0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021312500UqXmcxgrAW9Ki64.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131251pD5krjTBg3XNeZKJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131251WhwdrY2NSLJ3fP5D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131252WPAwSR9mVDFynavK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131252CyuEJoXRw0kiUG4c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>三楼有英国的音响品牌“天朗”（Tannoy）和音箱器材制作商 LINN 的音响。有书架放了一些经典的唱片，营造出一个居家的气氛。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131253ZI4o2N8UjQs1LuVc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021312536oFIGbSirg04nNKA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131254NPugZhmF5Sj0CY7i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131255GCsl460BXInSZVeR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Fred Perry 经典衬衫的版型从 1952 年就定好了，一直未变，Fred Perry 邀请过不少音乐人联名创造新款，在新店也成列了专为这次开店设计的“Tokyo Specials”。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131255D06UwRvgtfocaCzH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131256kcaQrY5RxM69sKtC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p>Tokyo Specials by Paul Weller</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131257jArPhoEZwWCzdcmV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p>Tokyo Specials by Terry Hall</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021312575hgiaClA41txGYpT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p>Tokyo Specials by Amy Winehouse</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021312583xFpTNza1sIPGCjt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p>Tokyo Specials by Don Letts</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131258knpAPem2I4KOxhgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p>Tokyo Specials by Damon Albarn</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021312590tVRDLQhxp7WAy1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p>Tokyo Specials by Art Comes First</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021312595jBEArZOCUtpNyae.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p>Tokyo Specials by Art Comes First</p></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p>Fred Perry 目前在全球有 130 多家门店，在中国内地通过代理方销售，没有正式的门店。</p>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/3/fred-perry-shop-tokyo-world-largest-flagship\">hypebeast</a>、<a href=\"http://www.fredperry.jp/news/2016/03/fred_perry_tokyo.php\">fredperry</a></p>\n<p>          </p>\n\n"}